 He said in an artifical voice. "I have no name. I am a gift from nature. I 
have no name. I am not one warrior but many. The more bot i meet the more 
bots i become. I am not an individual but a group. Just by seeing you i can 
do this." he transformed into the raven. "Check your scanners i have the 
exact signature of you. And no machine could tell the difference."
